 garlic cloves","5 g fresh root ginger, peeled, cut in round slices (2 mm)","1 red chilli, fresh, halved and deseeded","½ - 1 tsp dried fennel seeds, to taste","1 pinch ground cinnamon","¼ tsp saffron","½ tsp fine sea salt","3 Tbsp olive oil","2 white fish fillets, skinless (approx. 180 g each)"]},{"title":"Chermoula Sauce","content":["2 garlic cloves","30 g fresh coriander, leaves and stalks, cut in pieces","½ - 1 tsp ground cumin, to taste","1 tsp sweet paprika","1 pinch dried chilli flakes","30 g freshly squeezed lemon juice","30 g olive oil"]},{"title":"Couscous Salad","content":["100 g couscous","15 g olive oil","110 g water","1 pinch ground cumin","½ tsp salt","5 sprigs fresh coriander, leaves only","1 fresh red chilli","1 tsp lemon zest, finely grated","1 carrot (approx. 60 g), cut in pieces","50 g pitted black olives","80 g tinned chick peas, drained"]},{"title":"Steaming Marinated Fish","content":["500 g water"]}],"id":"r170303","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-wNMyC-YHvWc\/XZVRCayrv7I\/AAAAAAAAdJA\/HSVdwehTlKwQpubqmzn7Of3XqAJGKoTOACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_d_NdHpE1UlgPMSgE.png","title":"Marinated White Fish Fillets with Chermoula Sauce and Couscous Salad","publishedAt":"2017-05-29T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"43 g","fat":"45 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"44 g","calories":"3187 kJ \/ 762 kcal"},"usefulItems":"cling film, refrigerator","basicInfo":["medium","20m","1h 20m","2 portions"]}